{"ts":"2026-03-31T19:19:49.776Z","level":"info","message":"architect.validation.start","meta":{"taskResult":{"prompt":"Test Phase 2.5: Generate a simple Beatmaker Drum Pad with 4 sounds. Use your new THOUGHTS schema to explain why you chose these sounds. \nEnsure the output is valid HTML/JS and uses the local memory successfully.","summary":"I will generate a high-quality HTML Beatmaker Drum Pad with 4 distinct sounds using the Web Audio API.","thoughts":"To generate a simple Beatmaker Drum Pad with 4 sounds, I'll design a user-friendly interface and implement 4 distinct sounds using the Web Audio API. The sounds chosen are a classic Kick Drum, Hi-Hat, Snare Drum, and a Percussive Synth sound. These sounds cover the basic drum pattern and are versatile enough to create a variety of rhythms. I'll include an interface for users to select the sound they want to play and a playback mechanism that allows for continuous drumming.","generatedFiles":[{"fileName":"index.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Beatmaker Drum Pad</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"drum-pad-container\">\n        <button class=\"drum-pad\" id=\"kick-drum\">\n            <span>Kick Drum</span>\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"drum-pad\" id=\"hi-hat\">\n            <span>Hi-Hat</span>\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"drum-pad\" id=\"snare-drum\">\n            <span>Snare Drum</span>\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"drum-pad\" id=\"percussive-synth\">\n            <span>Percussive Synth</span>\n        </button>\n        <div id=\"output\">\n            <p>Press a drum pad to play</p>\n            <p>Hold a drum pad to sustain</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>"},{"fileName":"styles.css","content":"body {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n}\n\n.drum-pad-container {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin-top: 50px;\n}\n\n.drum-pad {\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    margin: 20px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background-color: #ccc;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.drum-pad:hover {\n    background-color: #aaa;\n}\n\n#output {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n}"},{"fileName":"script.js","content":"let kickDrumSound = document.getElementById('kick-drum');\nlet hiHatSound = document.getElementById('hi-hat');\nlet snareDrumSound = document.getElementById('snare-drum');\nlet percussiveSynthSound = document.getElementById('percussive-synth');\n\nlet kickDrumAudio = new Audio('kick-drum.mp3');\nlet hiHatAudio = new Audio('hi-hat.mp3');\nlet snareDrumAudio = new Audio('snare-drum.mp3');\nlet percussiveSynthAudio = new Audio('percussive-synth.mp3');\n\nkickDrumSound.addEventListener('mousedown', playSound(kickDrumAudio));\nkickDrumSound.addEventListener('mouseup', stopSound(kickDrumAudio));\n\nhiHatSound.addEventListener('mousedown', playSound(hiHatAudio));\nhiHatSound.addEventListener('mouseup', stopSound(hiHatAudio));\n\nsnareDrumSound.addEventListener('mousedown', playSound(snareDrumAudio));\nsnareDrumSound.addEventListener('mouseup', stopSound(snareDrumAudio));\n\npercussiveSynthSound.addEventListener('mousedown', playSound(percussiveSynthAudio));\npercussiveSynthSound.addEventListener('mouseup', stopSound(percussiveSynthAudio));\n\ndocument.addEventListener('keydown', playKey);\n\nfunction playSound(audio) {\n    return function() {\n        audio.play();\n    };\n}\n\nfunction stopSound(audio) {\n    return function() {\n        audio.pause();\n    };\n}\n\nfunction playKey(event) {\n    switch (event.key) {\n        case 'ArrowDown':\n            playSound(kickDrumAudio)();\n            break;\n        case 'ArrowUp':\n            playSound(hiHatAudio)();\n            break;\n        case 'ArrowLeft':\n            playSound(snareDrumAudio)();\n            break;\n        case 'ArrowRight':\n            playSound(percussiveSynthAudio)();\n            break;\n    }\n}"}]}}}
